entry.content:
To produce this issue, run below code in Chrome Canary:

```
const context = await navigator.ml.createContext({ deviceType: "gpu" });  
const builder = new MLGraphBuilder(context);  

const steps = 2;
const hidden_size = 2;
const batch_size = 1;

const inputTensorDesc = { dataType: "float32", dimensions: [steps, batch_size, 2] };  
const input = builder.input('input', inputTensorDesc); 

const weightTensorDesc = { dataType: "float32", dimensions: [1, 4 * hidden_size, 2] };  
const weight = builder.input('weight', weightTensorDesc); 

const recurrentWeightTensorDesc = { dataType: "float32", dimensions: [1, 4 * hidden_size, hidden_size] };  
const recurrentWeight = builder.input('recurrentWeight', recurrentWeightTensorDesc); 

const activation = builder.clamp();

const options = {
    activations: [activation, activation, activation]
};

const output = builder.lstm(input, weight, recurrentWeight, steps, hidden_size, options);

const graph = await builder.build({ 'A': output[0], 'B': output[1] }); 
```

It reaches `NOTREACHED_NORETURN()` in `GetActivationDmlDesc()`.

https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:services/webnn/dml/graph_impl.cc;l=490
